The paper deals with the problem of verifying data stored on a remote server, which is a common problem in computer security. The use of Kolmogorov complexity and list decoding suggests that the paper may fall under the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), information theory (cs.IT), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), or distributed computing (cs.DC).
